{
  "texts": [
    "For the systematic review, a comprehensive search was conducted to identify relevant literature on the integration of ChatGPT in mathematics teaching and learning.",
    "Google Scholar was utilized as the primary database due to its extensive coverage of academic articles and journals in various disciplines.",
    "The search strategy employed a combination of keywords related to 'ChatGPT,' 'mathematics education,' 'teaching,' and 'learning.'",
    "Boolean operators (AND, OR) were utilized to refine the search results.",
    "Moreover, citation chaining and reference list screening were employed to identify additional relevant studies."
  ]
}